{
  "_comment": [
    "field_dict.json — synonym dictionary for the SDF extraction pipeline.",
    "Each key is a canonical field name. Each value is a list of lowercase label",
    "strings that may appear in a PDF before the field's value.",
    "Rules:",
    "  - Add new fields by adding a new top-level key + synonym list.",
    "  - Synonyms are matched case-insensitively anywhere in a line.",
    "  - Longer synonyms are matched first, so be specific before being general.",
    "  - The pipeline also has built-in pattern strategies (revision numbers,",
    "    address blocks, headings) that do NOT need synonyms here.",
    "  - This file is merged with built-in defaults at runtime; you only need",
    "    to list NEW or ADDITIONAL synonyms for existing fields."
  ],

  "effective_date": [
    "effective date", "effective:", "eff date", "date effective",
    "document date", "letter date", "issued date",
    "date of issue", "issue date"
  ],

  "manufacturing_date": [
    "date of manufacture", "manufacturing date", "manufacture date",
    "mfg date", "mfg:", "date manufactured", "manufactured on",
    "date of manufacturing", "production date", "date of production",
    "manufacture:", "manufactured:", "date of mfg",
    "date manufactured on", "prod date"
  ],

  "vendor_name": [
